static MNodeType MindSpace::MNodeType::findNodeType ( const QString &  uuid,
const QString &  defineIfNotExists = "" 
) [inline, static]

Returns:
A MNodeType object of the given uuid if it exists. If the uuid does not exist, and defineIfNotExists is empty, then a null link type is returned. If the uuid does not exist, and defineIfNotExists is NOT empty, then a new MNodeType object with the given uuid and defineIfNotExists as the name is returned.
